{\pard\sb0\sa120\f0\fs22 GitHub READMEs look great {\i on GitHub}. But what about:\par}
{\pard\sb36\sa36\li480\fi-360\f0\fs22 \u8226?  :briefcase: {\b Sharing with non-developers} who don't have GitHub accounts?\par}
