{\pard\sb36\sa36\li480\fi-360\f0\fs22 \u8226?  :airplane: {\b Reading offline} without a browser?\par}
{\pard\sb36\sa36\li480\fi-360\f0\fs22 \u8226?  :printer: {\b Printing} with proper formatting?\par}
